Softbank Says It Doesn’t Plan to Acquire Yahoo Japan Shares

-- B y   Y o s h i n o r i   E k i
-- 
2011-03-02T03:23:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-02/softbank-says-it-doesn-t-plan-to-acquire-yahoo-japan-shares.html
  Softbank Corp . said it doesn’t
intend to buy shares of  Yahoo Japan Corp ., denying an earlier
media report.  Softbank is not having any discussions about acquiring
shares of Yahoo Japan, said Takeaki Nukii, a spokesman at the
Tokyo-based mobile-phone operator. Reuters earlier reported on
the talks.  To contact the reporter on this story:
